I have to take this.

01:14:23.001 --> 01:14:24.962
MAN: He must be from Bank of America.

01:14:25.045 --> 01:14:26.046
(ALL LAUGHING)

01:14:26.672 --> 01:14:29.341
- MAN: Our subprime department is fine.
