01:22:34.701 --> 01:22:36.870
Whoa, I just got really scared.

01:22:38.413 --> 01:22:40.332
First of all, great show today.

01:22:40.415 --> 01:22:41.875
- You were terrific.
- Thank you.

01:22:41.958 --> 01:22:43.585
Your big mouth was a revelation.

01:22:43.668 --> 01:22:45.378
I appreciate that.

01:22:45.503 --> 01:22:47.255
You worried you and your swaps
are getting played?

01:22:47.339 --> 01:22:50.467
Well, this is an opportunity for you
to meet who you're betting against.

01:22:50.550 --> 01:22:52.344
