don't you, Mr. Baum?

01:28:14.082 --> 01:28:18.002
But, apparently,
society values me very much.

01:28:19.045 --> 01:28:20.797
In fact, let's do this.

01:28:22.840 --> 01:28:25.843
I'll tell you how much I'm worth.

01:28:26.386 --> 01:28:27.887
