01:28:29.097 --> 01:28:34.185
God, you are an incredibly
big piece of shit.

01:28:39.941 --> 01:28:41.818
Short everything that guy has touched.

01:28:41.901 --> 01:28:43.528
I want half a billion more in swaps.

01:28:44.070 --> 01:28:46.280
