01:30:24.003 --> 01:30:25.588
I'm a banker. I'm a part of it.

01:30:25.671 --> 01:30:27.965
You always have, Mark.
Like you're untainted.

01:30:28.049 --> 01:30:31.511
It changed me.
It changed me into a person

01:30:32.095 --> 01:30:33.930
who is not able to
reach out to someone...

01:30:34.013 --> 01:30:35.932
He was in pain.
My brother was in real pain.

01:30:36.516 --> 01:30:38.851
There's no perfect way to help.

01:30:41.854 --> 01:30:44.315
It's sad. It's scary.

01:30:44.440 --> 01:30:47.610
So stop trying to fix the world.

01:30:47.693 --> 01:30:48.778
He told me...

01:30:48.861 --> 01:30:50.196
You're not a saint.

01:30:50.279 --> 01:30:52.031
