01:30:52.240 --> 01:30:53.866
...that he was having bad thoughts.

01:30:53.950 --> 01:30:56.744
CYNTHIA: Just feel the feelings
like the rest of us.

01:30:57.078 --> 01:31:01.249
MARK: <i>My first response
was to offer him some money.</i>

01:31:01.582 --> 01:31:04.085
<i>I offered him fucking money!</i>

01:31:04.502 --> 01:31:06.129
(INAUDIBLE)

01:31:09.757 --> 01:31:12.385
His face was so smashed.

01:31:23.771 --> 01:31:25.565
(SOBBING)

01:31:31.445 --> 01:31:32.780
That's right.

01:31:44.292 --> 01:31:45.543
(ROCK MUSIC PLAYING)

01:31:45.668 --> 01:31:46.919
(MOANING)

01:32:29.921 --> 01:32:32.215
(SCREAMING)

01:32:39.472 --> 01:32:40.806
MIKE'S WIFE: Michael?

01:32:40.890 --> 01:32:42.225
- Michael?
- Yes. Yes.

01:32:42.308 --> 01:32:44.393
- Is everything okay?
- Yes, honey.

01:32:44.477 --> 01:32:46.604
- You sure?
- Yeah, baby.

01:32:48.397 --> 01:32:49.690
I'm fine. (LAUGHS)

01:32:58.658 --> 01:33:00.326
MIKE: <i>To all investors.</i>

01:33:00.409 --> 01:33:01.494
<i>As you may know,</i>

01:33:02.495 --> 01:33:06.082
<i>our agreement allows me
to take extraordinary measures</i>

01:33:06.540 --> 01:33:09.460
<i>when markets
aren't functioning properly.</i>

01:33:09.543 --> 01:33:13.256
<i>I currently have reason to
believe the mortgage bond market</i>

01:33:13.923 --> 01:33:15.675
<i>is fraudulent.</i>

01:33:17.843 --> 01:33:22.598
<i>So, in order to protect investors
from this fraudulent market,</i>

01:33:22.682 --> 01:33:25.935
<i>I've decided to restrict
investors' withdrawals</i>

01:33:26.018 --> 01:33:27.687
<i>until further notice.</i>

01:33:28.020 --> 01:33:31.691
<i>Sincerely, Dr. Michael J. Burry.</i>

01:33:41.117 --> 01:33:42.868
(HEAVY METAL MUSIC PLAYING)

01:33:43.703 --> 01:33:44.996
