<i>The principal source
of the slowdown in economic growth...</i>

01:35:29.475 --> 01:35:31.519
Time and time and time again,

01:35:31.644 --> 01:35:33.771
I have gone to bat for you, Mark!

01:35:33.854 --> 01:35:35.147
We've known each other
for seven years...

01:35:35.231 --> 01:35:37.566
She's got some lungs on her.
I'm impressed.

01:35:38.734 --> 01:35:40.569
